                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tBtgxlapE2o">
                    <div class="panel-body"><img src="/images/CEO/CEO_AD2.jpg" class="img-responsive" style="width:100%"
                                                 alt="Image"></div>
                </a>
                <div class="panel-footer">신출내기 공연 기획자를 위한 성공특강!</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="panel panel-success">
                <div class="panel-heading">최신기사</div>
                <a href="http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/culture/2018/06/01/0901000000AKR20180601191800013.HTML">
                    <div class="panel-body"><img src="/images/CEO/CEO_AD3.jpg" class="img-responsive" style="width:100%"
                                                 alt="Image"></div>
                </a>
                <div class="panel-footer">아티스트와 함께하는 예술 영화 감상</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<br>


</div>
</div><br><br>


<footer class="container-fluid text-left">
    <a href="/">
        <button>LINKES 메인 페이지로</button>
    </a>
    <br><br>
    <p>Software Engineering Project </p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
